Bakandamiya BMI is an app designed to provide a basic tool
        for measuring body mass index. It is meant to serve as a preliminary step to stay healthy and make informed medical decisions. It is never a substitute for medical prescription,
        so it should be used in consultation with medical personnel.\n\nThe app is created by Bakandamiya, a technology and content development company based in Nigeria. It is free for all to use.
